$eref.description: Holds attributes of an ANS collection - a common parent to story and gallery objects.
$eref.title: A collection of content.

___content_elements.description: List of the content elements in this collection.

___count.description: Total number of items in the source that this list pulls from

___next.description: A page number, story id, url, or other parameter used for retrieving subsequent items in the list

___previous.description: A page number, story id, url, or other parameter used for retrieving previous items in the list

description: A set of summary items to be displayed together (e.g., landing pages, query results, etc.)
